column5: We had 252 visitors online at 12:31...a new record. Why aren't y'all working???
WOW!!!  Thats awesome.. Ive seen it where we were close before... must be all this spring weather!!!
We are all at work!  lol
Great stuff Rick and I'm happy to know I was 1 / 252 of the record
The guys are saying to me "just what the heck are you looking at?" Way to go OFC
Im at work lol...wish i was on the water
i was on the water, great that i wasn't at work !
Of course I'm working....I would be on OFC if I was wasn't.....lol
LOL I thought you were going to sing!
i say, we should have a "work version of OFC". One that only shows text and looks like a spreadsheet or some sort so it looks work related haha.  I'm glad that my bosses don't fish.
Victor..use the RSS  feed or the Lo-Fi version and it will apear as you requested.
Dang, I geuss that means there will be 252 people at my trout spot tomorrow...
I'm still at work LOL !!!!  I love this site  . However,it's very addicting. I can't help sponging all this great info up. Thanks guys!
I knew if enough people spread a rumour of nekkid women fishing live on here it would bring in the crowds.
It wasnt me, I was working hard!
Same here. I was working and didn't log on at that time. Nice to hear of the large numbers logging on though.
I see.  So lots o' folks weren't really even trying.  Lightweights.
okay so back up here  WHAT IS WORK I have forgotten what that is   vance
